description.en:
Little Doge is a MemeCoin on the Binance Smart Chain. Little Doge was inspired by Everrise and Doge.
Each transaction distributes 6 % into the buyback wallet. 2 % are distributed to the holders and 3 % of each transaction are distributed into the marketing wallet.
After each sell there is a buyback from the buyback wallet which is called BIG DOGE. The amount of the buyback can be customized.
